{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Kiara St. James (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that transgender activist <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kiara_St._James\" title=\"Kiara St. James\">Kiara St.<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">&nbsp;</span>James</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> helped to end New York's <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walking_While_Trans\" title=\"Walking While Trans\">Walking While Trans</a></b> law?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kiara_St._James","retrieved":1784187341243},{"title":"a formerly best-selling title in the Fate franchise (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fate/Extra_CCC\" title=\"Fate/Extra CCC\">a formerly best-selling title in the <i>Fate</i> franchise</a></b> remained exclusive to Japan until an English fan translation was released a decade later?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fate/Extra_CCC","retrieved":1784187341245},{"title":"Katrin Bennhold (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that German-born <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katrin_Bennhold\" title=\"Katrin Bennhold\">Katrin Bennhold</a></b> has been a senior writer for <i>The New York Times</i> in three European capitals?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katrin_Bennhold","retrieved":1784187341249},{"title":"their own TV station (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the school board of Charlotte, North Carolina, bought a defunct TV station in Florida and moved its equipment to start <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WTVI\" title=\"WTVI\">their own TV station</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WTVI","retrieved":1784187341250},{"title":"Torreón del Monje (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Torreón_del_Monje\" title=\"Torreón del Monje\">Torreón del Monje</a></b> was the headquarters of a pigeon-shooting club?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Torre%C3%B3n_del_Monje","retrieved":1784187341252},{"title":"Marvin Lowenthal (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvin_Lowenthal\" title=\"Marvin Lowenthal\">Marvin Lowenthal</a></b> went from being a silk-mill <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobbin_boy\" title=\"Bobbin boy\">bobbin boy</a> to writing <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Jews_of_Germany\" title=\"The Jews of Germany\">a sixteen-century history of Jews in Germany</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvin_Lowenthal","retrieved":1784187341257},{"title":"Kreni-Promeni (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kreni-Promeni\" title=\"Kreni-Promeni\">Kreni-Promeni</a></b> activists put up a billboard in Belgrade with attached cotton lungs that gradually darkened as they absorbed polluted air?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kreni-Promeni","retrieved":1784187341257},{"title":"a Japanese show that aimed to encourage entrepreneurship (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <i><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shark_Tank\" title=\"Shark Tank\">Shark Tank</a></i> was adapted from <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manē_no_Tora\" title=\"Manē no Tora\">a Japanese show that aimed to encourage entrepreneurship</a></b> during <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lost_Decades\" title=\"Lost Decades\">a lengthy period of economic stagnation in the Japanese economy</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Man%C4%93_no_Tora","retrieved":1784187341269},{"title":"John Gauntlett (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Gauntlett\" title=\"John Gauntlett\">John 